      "body" : "Concept ACK\r\n\r\nSince i2p is added in Bitcoin Core which uses a different proxy, it's better if both are shared in `-getinfo`\r\n\r\n`-i2psam` is used for proxy and incoming both as documented in [doc/i2p.md](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/doc/i2p.md)",
